  <name>openHAB Add-ons :: Bundles :: Free@Home Binding</name>

  <description>This binding currently supports:

    SysAP connection
    Scene activation
    Raffstore/Shutter control: stepwise and complete incl. raffstore groups
    Switch
    Dimmer
    Thermostat
    4.3" Touch with integrated Thermostat
    Weather station
and
    Discovery

Events of the physical devices are fed back to binding.</description>
